# Git sync (poi-filter-testing)

This repo must stay aligned with https://github.com/motormouthvis/poi-filter-testing.

- **Start of work:** run `git pull --ff-only origin main` (or `.\scripts\sync.ps1` before editing if you will push).
- **End of work / after file changes:** run `.\scripts\sync.ps1` so all files are committed and pushed.
- Do not leave untracked project files in this repo; add and push them.
- Only `.gitignore` exclusions (secrets, caches) stay local — not arbitrary doc or script files.
